= SDL_CreateCond =
Use this function to create a condition variable.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_cond* SDL_CreateCond(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns ^a pointer to the SDL_cond structure that is created / filled with the condition variable^.

== Code Examples ==
*
```c++
SDL_cond *cond;

cond=SDL_CreateCond();
.
.
/* Do stuff */
.
.
SDL_DestroyCond(cond);
```
